column5:
All the feature-length movies I fully watched in 2020. There were plenty of movies that I started but never finished, but since I didn't finish them I didn't add them to the list. I don't think I'll ever watch this many movies in a single year, I have mostly quarantine to thank for my final count.

+7 films to the current total due to rewatches. (Airplane, Grown-Ups, Nightcrawler, Ferris Bueller's Day Off, Parasite, Election, Rise of Skywalker)
